gines, the aircraft encountered severe icing, turbulence or other difficulty which led to the loss of control by the crew. It could not be determined why the aircraft was 12 miles south of the assigned airway. The plane crashed high into Mount Slesse. The bodies and wreckage were not found until 05/12/1957 and the wreckage still remains at the site which is now a memorial.','Near Chilliwack, British Columbia, Canada',9,1956,12,'winter',0),(1875,'1956-12-12 00:00:00','Dannemois, France','Air France','Vickers 708 Viscount',5,5,0,'Crashed in a steep angle of attack.','Dannemois, France',12,1956,12,'winter',0),(1876,'1956-12-22 00:00:00','Grub, Germany','JAT Yugoslav Airlines','Convair CV-340-58',30,3,0,'The co-pilot acting as pilot-in-command and under the instruction of the captain began a descent to land until the aircraft hit the ground, left wing first. Both wings detached and the fuselage slid 1,200 feet.','Grub, Germany',22,1956,12,'winter',27),(1877,'1956-12-22 00:00:00','Grub, Germany','JAT Yugoslav Airlines','Convair CV-340-58',30,3,0,'The co-pilot acting as pilot-in-command and under the instruction of the captain began a descent to land until the aircraft hit the ground, left wing first. Both wings detached and the fuselage slid 1,200 feet.','Mt. Giner, Italy',22,1956,12,'winter',27),(1878,'1956-12-22 00:00:00','Mt. Giner, Italy','Linee Aeree Italiane','Douglas DC-3',21,21,0,'The aircraft strayed off the assigned airway and hit a mountain. The pilot did not follow the airways assigned in the flight plan. He did not check his direction and position along the new route. Pilot error.','Grub, Germany',22,1956,12,'winter',0),(1879,'1956-12-22 00:00:00','Mt. Giner, Italy','Linee Aeree Italiane','Douglas DC-3',21,21,0,'The aircraft strayed off the assigned airway and hit a mountain. The pilot did not follow the airways assigned in the flight plan. He did not check his direction and position along the new route. Pilot error.','Mt. Giner, Italy',22,1956,12,'winter',0