ec Canada',22,1960,9,'autumn',0),(2182,'1960-09-22 00:00:00','Campbell Lake, Quebec Canada','Wheeler Airlines','Noorduyn Norseman',4,3,0,'Shortly after takeoff from Campbell Lake, while climbing, the single engine aircraft stalled and crashed in flames in a wooded area. The pilot and two passengers were killed while a third passenger was seriously injured.  Engine failure.','Off Naha, Okinawa',22,1960,9,'autumn',1),(2183,'1960-09-22 00:00:00','Campbell Lake, Quebec Canada','Wheeler Airlines','Noorduyn Norseman',4,3,0,'Shortly after takeoff from Campbell Lake, while climbing, the single engine aircraft stalled and crashed in flames in a wooded area. The pilot and two passengers were killed while a third passenger was seriously injured.  Engine failure.','Campbell Lake, Quebec Canada',22,1960,9,'autumn',1),(2184,'1960-09-26 00:00:00','Moscow, Russia','Austrian Airlines','Vickers Viscount 837',37,31,0,'Crashed on approach to Moscow, 11 nm short of the runway. Malfunctioning or misread altimeter.','Moscow, Russia',26,1960,9,'autumn',6),(2185,'1960-09-28 00:00:00','Near Juchetipec, Mexico','Mexicana','Douglas DC-3 (C-53-DO)',18,8,0,'Crashed on the slopes of a mountain near Juchitepec, about 40 km south of Mexico City Airport in dense fog.','Near Juchetipec, Mexico',28,1960,9,'autumn',10),(2186,'1960-09-29 00:00:00','Off Elba, Italy','United Arab Airlines','Vickers Viscount 739B',21,21,0,'Crashed  into the Tyrrhenian Sea off Elba after penetrating severe thunderstorm.','Off Elba, Italy',29,1960,9,'autumn',0),(2187,'1960-10-04 00:00:00','Boston, Massachusetts','Eastern Air Lines','Lockheed 188A Electra',72,62,0,'A few seconds after becoming airborne, the aircraft struck a flock of starlings. A number of these birds were ingested in engines No. 1, 2, and 4.  Engine No. 1 was shut down and its propeller was feathered. Engines No. 2 and 4 experienced a substantial momentary loss of power. This abrupt and intermittent loss and recovery of power resulted in the aircraft yawing 