 entire hydraulic control system, including the system used to open the rear door was not working, as burning fuel gushed into the cabin trapping people inside. This is the worst helicopter disaster in aviation history.','Khankala, Chechnya',19,2002,8,'summer',26),(5371,'2002-08-22 00:00:00','Pokhara, Nepal','Shangri La Air','de Havilland Canada DHC-6-300 Twin Otter',18,18,0,'The plane crashed into a hill 3 miles southeast of Pokhara Airport while on approach. The plane broke into several pieces and bodies and wreckage was scattered over a small area. There was poor weather in the area at the time of the accident. Controlled flight into terrain.','Pokhara, Nepal',22,2002,8,'summer',0),(5372,'2002-08-29 00:00:00','Near Ayan, Russia','Vostok Aviakompania','Antonov AN-28',16,16,0,'The twin prop plane crashed into a cliff in dense fog as it prepared to land at Ayan. ATC lost contact with the aircraft 12 minutes before it was scheduled to land.  The crew made four attempts to land before disappearing off radar. Crew error.','Near Ayan, Russia',29,2002,8,'summer',0),(5373,'2002-08-30 00:00:00','Rio Branco, Brazil','Rico Taxi Aéreo','Embraer 120ER Brasilia',31,23,0,'The plane crashed about 1 mile short of the runway in heavy rain and strong winds while attempting to land at Rio Branco Airport. Congressman Ildefonso Cordeiro was among the victims.','Lexington, Kentucky',30,2002,8,'summer',8),(5374,'2002-08-30 00:00:00','Rio Branco, Brazil','Rico Taxi Aéreo','Embraer 120ER Brasilia',31,23,0,'The plane crashed about 1 mile short of the runway in heavy rain and strong winds while attempting to land at Rio Branco Airport. Congressman Ildefonso Cordeiro was among the victims.','Rio Branco, Brazil',30,2002,8,'summer',8),(5375,'2002-09-14 00:00:00','Paranapanema, Sao Paulo, Brazil','Total  Air Lines','ATR 42-300',2,2,0,'One hour after the takeoff , the the plane disappeared of  Curitiba  ATC. The wreckage was found on a farm, around a crater. Unknown cause.','Paranapanema, Sao Pau